title: Kristen Stewart poses for provacative photo
text:
Published October 18, 2015 Facebook 0 Twitter 0 Email Print September 5, 2015. Kristen Stewart attends a photocall for "Equals" during the 72nd Venice Film Festival at Palazzo del Casino in Venice, Italy. (2015 Getty Images)
Do we spot a smile there, Kristen Stewart? Well, it's definitely a smirk…
The normally demure actress has gone nearly nude for a photo series by famed photographer Mario Testino, which he's aptly named "Towel Series."

He shared his latest black-and-white portrait on Saturday, which featured a naked Stewart covered by nothing but a white towel loosely draped over her right shoulder. A peek of her left shoulder and right butt cheek can be seen as she lifts her right arm behind her head and masks her exposed breast with the other hand.
The 90 other women and men who've been featured include Blake Lively, Justin Bieber, Kendall Jenner and Keira Knightley.
